<h2 id="toc1"><span>&#8212;</span></h2>
<div class="showcase">
<p>Because somehow, Egyptian gods, the SPC universe, mysterious soul-vacuum devices, bad puns, and seagull scientists can all happily coexist in the same storyline. No wonder they called themselves Team Bird, the plot brainstorming must have been done while everyone was hella high.</p>
